item.title: Easy question so read this please! thank YOU
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“spitsen, post:3, topic:418073”][quote author=zyle1992 link=topic=520621.msg3781464#msg3781464 date=1318524901]

hello i started a online rs private server so it works good…at the evening i go to bed and the next morging…i run the server i check no-ip everthing is fine but it said server is offline WTF???

Go to http://www.canyouseeme.org/
Type in your server port number
Click check.

If it says that it cannot see your computer, then you have not forwarded your ports correctly.
[/quote]

i did it its said error cant find your service i ported me router…firewall…no-ip its strange a day early everthings just works fine i didnt change anything…[/quote]

Things don’t “just happen”. Well, perhaps in quantum mechanics, but not here.

Either it worked, and you changed it, and don’t believe that what you changed could cause the problem
Or you didn’t have it working, and you told us you did so that someone will fix it for you.
